desc: Displays a list of popular extensions in the Extensions view.
Displays a list of recommended extensions in the Extensions view.
Opens the Extensions view to show recently published extensions in the Marketplace.
Lists all built-in extensions in the Extensions view.
Opens the Extensions view to show recently updates for installed extensions.
Lists all extensions that are not supported in the current workspace.
Displays a list of all enabled extensions in Visual Studio Code.
Displays a list of all disabled extensions in the Extensions view.
Clears the search results in the Extensions view.
Refreshes the list of extensions in the Extensions view.
Focuses on the list of installed extensions within the Extensions view.
Focuses on the 'Popular' section within the Extensions view in VS Code.
Focuses on the enabled extensions view in the Extensions sidebar.
Focuses on the view of disabled extensions within Visual Studio Code.
Focuses the search box in the Extensions view to search among installed extensions.
Focuses the search box in the Extensions view to search among enabled extensions.
Focuses on the search box in the Extensions view with disabled extensions filter applied.
Focuses the search box in the Extensions view to filter for outdated extensions available updated.
Focuses the search box in the built-in extensions view.
Focuses the input field for searching extensions that are not supported in the current workspace in VS Code.
Focuses on the workspace recommendations view in the Extensions sidebar.
Show featured extensions in the Extensions sidebar.
Focuses on the built-in feature extensions view in the Extensions sidebar in VS Code.
Sorts the extensions by the number of installations.
Sorts the extensions alphabetically by their names.
Sorts the extensions by their publication date.
Sorts the extensions based on their user ratings.
Sorts the extensions by their last updated date.
